Summary: saw very faint light moving very fast then noticed another thought it was a satilite but was moving to fast saw 6 in total moving in different directions then saw what looked like a shooting star moving upward in the sky very bright
trends: There have been no other sightings in Munds Park
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: Sighting Detailsme and my wife were walking our dogs when we noticed a star that appeared to be moving at first we thought it was a satelite but it was moving very fast then my wife noticed another moving north at the same time we noticed another traveling south it appeared to pass the one going north the color of these lights was very faint but would randomly flash very bright for a second or two but very unfrequently we witnessed 6 of these lights 2 going south two going north and one going east and then turn north and one going south east there was no noise what so ever there were military planes flying one looked to be following one of the lights going north all flying faster than sound i came inside to see if there was anything online at this time my wife looked out side and yelled at me to look at what looked like a shooting star except it was traveling up in a vertical path then dissapeared we were very excited and confused at what we were seeing still are
